# keybr-music Project Context

This is a fork of keybr.com (typing practice app) being adapted for musical instrument practice, starting with bandoneon.

## Key Concept

Detected pitches map to `CodePoint` values (MIDI note numbers). The existing keybr pipeline (`Step` -> `Histogram` -> `KeyStatsMap` -> lesson progression) works with pitches without modification because `Letter`, `Step`, and `Histogram` are keyed by `CodePoint`.

## New Packages (music-specific)

- `packages/keybr-pitch-detection/` -- Web Audio YIN pitch detector with noise floor gating
- `packages/keybr-instrument/` -- Note/Letter mapping and instrument definitions
- `packages/page-pitch-test/` -- Test page for live pitch detection at `/pitch-test`

